### Valid predict request
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "FastAPI is pleasant",
  "mode": "careful",
  "temperature": 0.2
}

### Invalid predict request: text too short and mode not allowed
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "hi",
  "mode": "slow",
  "temperature": 2
}
